# LOOKSMAXX Technical Specifications

## Overview
LOOKSMAXX is a facial analysis web application that provides users with detailed facial metrics, attractiveness scoring, and personalized improvement recommendations based on uploaded photos.

## User Flow

### 1. Landing Page (/)
- Hero section with app introduction
- Feature highlights (AI-powered analysis, detailed metrics, personalized recommendations)
- CTA button → Login/Signup

### 2. Authentication (/login)
- Email/Password login
- OAuth options (Google, Apple)
- Link to signup for new users

### 3. Photo Upload Flow (/upload)
After authentication, users go through a multi-step upload process:

#### Step 1: Gender Selection
- Male/Female toggle
- Affects analysis algorithms and scoring benchmarks

#### Step 2: Ethnicity Selection
- Dropdown with ethnic categories
- Used for population-specific beauty standards
- Options: Caucasian, Asian, African, Hispanic, Middle Eastern, South Asian, Mixed/Other

#### Step 3: Photo Upload
- Drag & drop or click to upload
- Guidelines displayed:
  - Front-facing photo
  - Neutral expression
  - Good lighting
  - No glasses/accessories
- Image preview before submission
- Crop/adjust functionality

### 4. Analysis Results (/analysis)
After processing, display comprehensive results:

#### Overall Score Section
- Large circular score display (0-10 scale)
- Percentile ranking ("Top X% of [gender] faces")
- Color-coded rating (Poor → Average → Good → Excellent)

#### Detailed Metrics Breakdown
Categories with individual scores:

**Facial Symmetry (0-10)**
- Left-right deviation percentage
- Key symmetry points analyzed

**Facial Proportions (0-10)**
- Thirds ratio (forehead, midface, lower face)
- Golden ratio adherence
- Facial width-to-height ratio

**Eye Area (0-10)**
- Canthal tilt (positive/negative degrees)
- Eye spacing (interpupillary distance)
- Eye shape analysis
- Eyebrow position

**Nose (0-10)**
- Nasofrontal angle
- Nasolabial angle
- Nose width ratio
- Bridge analysis

**Jaw & Chin (0-10)**
- Gonial angle
- Jaw width
- Chin projection
- Mandibular definition

**Lips & Mouth (0-10)**
- Lip ratio (upper to lower)
- Mouth width
- Smile analysis (if applicable)

**Skin Quality (0-10)**
- Clarity score
- Texture analysis
- Color evenness

#### Improvement Recommendations
- Prioritized list based on lowest-scoring areas
- Actionable suggestions (skincare, grooming, potential procedures)
- Before/after potential visualizations

#### Export/Share Options
- Download detailed PDF report
- Share results (with privacy controls)
- Save to profile history

## Technical Architecture

### Frontend (Next.js 14)
```
/src
  /app
    /page.tsx (Landing)
    /login/page.tsx
    /upload/page.tsx
    /analysis/page.tsx
  /components
    /ui (shadcn components)
    /features (feature-specific components)
  /lib
    /api (API client functions)
    /utils (helper functions)
  /hooks (custom React hooks)
  /types (TypeScript definitions)
```

### State Management
- React Context for global state (user, analysis results)
- Local state for form handling
- URL state for shareable analysis links

### API Integration
- RESTful API endpoints
- Image upload to cloud storage (S3/Cloudinary)
- Analysis processing queue
- Webhook for completion notification

### Key Dependencies
- next: 14.x
- react: 18.x
- tailwindcss: 3.x
- framer-motion: animations
- lucide-react: icons
- react-dropzone: file uploads
- recharts: data visualization

## UI/UX Guidelines

### Design System
- Dark theme primary (sophisticated, modern)
- Accent color: Electric blue (#3B82F6) or Gold (#F59E0B)
- Clean, minimal aesthetic
- Smooth animations and transitions

### Typography
- Headings: Geist Sans (bold weights)
- Body: Geist Sans (regular)
- Monospace: Geist Mono (for metrics/numbers)

### Components
- Cards with subtle gradients
- Glassmorphism effects for overlays
- Progress indicators for multi-step flows
- Skeleton loaders during analysis

### Responsive Design
- Mobile-first approach
- Breakpoints: sm(640), md(768), lg(1024), xl(1280)
- Touch-friendly interactions

## Data Models

### User
```typescript
interface User {
  id: string;
  email: string;
  name: string;
  createdAt: Date;
  analyses: Analysis[];
}
```

### Analysis
```typescript
interface Analysis {
  id: string;
  userId: string;
  imageUrl: string;
  gender: 'male' | 'female';
  ethnicity: string;
  overallScore: number;
  metrics: FacialMetrics;
  recommendations: Recommendation[];
  createdAt: Date;
}
```

### FacialMetrics
```typescript
interface FacialMetrics {
  symmetry: MetricScore;
  proportions: MetricScore;
  eyes: MetricScore;
  nose: MetricScore;
  jawChin: MetricScore;
  lipsMouth: MetricScore;
  skinQuality: MetricScore;
}

interface MetricScore {
  score: number;
  details: Record<string, number | string>;
  analysis: string;
}
```

## Security Considerations
- Secure image storage with expiring URLs
- User consent for photo processing
- Option to delete all data
- GDPR compliance considerations
- Rate limiting on analysis requests

## Performance Targets
- Landing page: < 1s LCP
- Image upload: Progress feedback
- Analysis processing: < 30s (with loading state)
- Results page: Smooth 60fps animations
</result>

